Package algorithms.graphs

Class NewmanGMLParser

java.lang.Object
algorithms.graphs.NewmanGMLParser
public class NewmanGMLParser extends Object
rough reduced function parser built to read a few of the GML files from http://www-personal.umich.edu/~mejn/netdata/ into a graph. the GML format is from: "GML: A portable Graph File Format" by Michael Himsolt http://openmis.ru/doc/clang/gml-tr.html NOTE: if one wanted to define all required and optional attributes, could make a more formal parser using ANTLR at antlr.org
Author:
nichole
